message.body: I hope it's not too weird of me to ask, but are you okay? You seemed not yourself tonight.
(1/2)No it's ok to ask, but I didn't realize I was off. I'm usually a little quieter around new people until I get a sense of how obnoxious I can be :) what
Well now I know :) next time I promise to be more inappropriate. When are tot heading out?
Working a half day tomorrow, then flying out. Technically I'm back Sunday, but just to sleep before heading to CT Monday. I'm tired just thinking about it.
Well get some rest and have a safe trip.
